OL,4,CAmazon apologises for wrongly denying
OL,5,Cdrivers need to urinate in bottles
OL,6, Amazon has apologised to a US
OL,7, politician for falsely denying that
OL,8, drivers are, at times, forced to
OL,9, urinate in plastic bottles.
OL,11,FMark Pocan, a Democrat from Wisconsin,
OL,12,Freferenced Amazon making "workers
OL,13,Furinate in water bottles" in a tweet.
OL,15,FThe official Amazon Twitter account
OL,16,Fthen replied: "If that were true,
OL,17,Fnobody would work for us."
OL,19,FThe company has now apologised after
OL,20,Fevidence emerged of drivers having to
OL,21,Furinate in bottles.
